articles.title: Navigating the Unknown
articles.description: Feeling stuck in your career?  This inspiring story follows one hospitality pro's journey from doubt-filled beginner to building a music library app in a coding bootcamp. Learn how they overcame imposter syndrome and discovered the power of collaboration. Click to find out if coding could be your next adventure!
